text: Willadele GivensAdele Givens: Still "Such A Lady" at 60! - BlackDoctor.org - Where Wellness & Culture Connect is an American comedian, actress, and writer. She is from Chicago, Illinois. She has had this career from 1989 to now. She has appeared in the shows The Hughleys, Moesha, The Parkers, Central Comedy Presents, and more. ==References== Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:American movie actors Category:Actors from Chicago Category:Comedians from Chicago Category:1960 births
